----Blue team----Name----------------Duty-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------Note------------------
-----------------SECURITY ANALYST----monitoring security logs, responding to SIEM events, and performing security ticket handling-------------------------------------------------------------------------------全天候，轮班，单位需要提供培训
-----------------FORENSIC ANALYST----recovering hidden and deleted data from hard drives, memory, mobile device, and network forensics--------------------------------------------------------------------------了解操作系统、驱动和内存
-----------------INCIDENT RESPONDER--When events occurs, coordinate the response and recovery teams, establishe a timeline of what happened, and figure out how to respond to it with the aid of others---------良好的分析、组织和沟通能力。领导力
-----------------MALWARE ANALYST-----run the malware in a sandbox and carefully analyze system changes and traffic. static analysis of the code itself----------------------------------------------------------Strong programming and network traffic analysis skills. understand assembly and programming architecture well
-----------------SECURITY ENGINEER---manage and update security appliances and rulesets. keep data storage, tools (manage SIEMs and security log aggregation tools). scripting new tools and API integrations.--systems administration skills, in Windows, CentOS, and Linux. Strong scripting skills. general knowledge of security operations, practices, and applications
